WEBVTT

00:42.042 --> 00:44.000
[ SIGHS ]

00:51.921 --> 00:52.922
EXCUSE ME.

00:52.922 --> 00:53.966
SURE.

00:59.537 --> 01:02.062
[ SPEAKING
INDISTINCTLY ]

01:14.596 --> 01:16.206
OH.
OH.

01:16.206 --> 01:17.555
LET ME CALL YOU BACK,
OKAY?HERE YOU GO.

01:17.555 --> 01:19.427
THANK YOU.
THANK YOU SO MUCH.

01:19.427 --> 01:21.037
[ BABY CRYING ]

01:21.037 --> 01:23.431
[ MAN SPEAKING
OVER LOUDSPEAKER ]

01:31.395 --> 01:32.744
THANKS A LOT.HAVE A NICE DAY.

01:32.744 --> 01:34.485
HAVE A NICE DAY.

01:37.575 --> 01:39.751
[ PEOPLE SCREAMING ]

01:48.586 --> 01:51.459
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

02:12.306 --> 02:14.351
MORNING, JANE.

02:14.351 --> 02:17.659
CAB TO A CRIME SCENE?
THAT'S VERY COSMOPOLITAN OF YOU.

02:17.659 --> 02:19.226
WELL, MY CAR
WOULDN'T START.

02:19.226 --> 02:20.792
WELL, OF COURSE
IT WOULDN'T.

02:20.792 --> 02:22.925
HOW WAS YOUR DATE
WITH AGENT PIKE?

02:22.925 --> 02:24.056
IT WAS OKAY.

02:24.056 --> 02:26.320
MM. JUST OKAY?

02:26.320 --> 02:27.625
IT WENT WELL.

02:27.625 --> 02:29.497
GOOD, HUH?
OH, WELL, THAT'S GREAT.

02:29.497 --> 02:31.194
THAT'S GREAT.
EXCELLENT.

02:31.194 --> 02:34.023
HEY. THE HOSPITAL SAYS
THERE'S ONLY ONE DEATH.

02:34.023 --> 02:35.764
HE WAS RIGHT NEXT TO THE BOMB
WHEN IT WENT OFF.

02:35.764 --> 02:36.895
COULD HAVE BEEN
A LOT WORSE.

02:36.895 --> 02:37.983
HOW MANY INJURIES?

02:37.983 --> 02:38.854
FOUR,
BUT ONLY ONE SERIOUS --

02:38.854 --> 02:40.551
A HOMELESS MAN.

02:40.551 --> 02:42.379
THEY THINK
HE'S GONNA PULL THROUGH.THAT'S LUCKY.

02:42.379 --> 02:44.773
YEAH. THE EYEWITNESSES AGREE
THAT THE BOMB WENT OFF

02:44.773 --> 02:47.036
IN FRONT OF THE KIOSK
JUST AFTER THE BUS PULLED OUT,

02:47.036 --> 02:49.125
BUT SO FAR, NO ONE'S BEEN ABLE
TO I.D. A BOMBER.

02:49.125 --> 02:51.475
WELL, HE PROBABLY
GOT ON THE BUS.

02:51.475 --> 02:52.824
DID THE FIRST RESPONDERS
GET A LIST OF THE PASSENGERS?

02:52.824 --> 02:54.478
A FEW.
IT WAS CHAOS.

02:54.478 --> 02:56.480
WE'RE HOPING TO PULL SOME
SECURITY FOOTAGE FROM THE AREA.

02:56.480 --> 02:58.830
ANYTHING YOU FIND,
MAKE SURE YOU SHARE IT

02:58.830 --> 03:00.702
WITH THE JOINT TERRORIST
TASK FORCE.

03:00.702 --> 03:02.486
THEY'RE GONNA LOOK
AT THEIR CRIMES

03:02.486 --> 03:04.227
AND SEE IF THERE'S ANYTHING
THAT FIT WITH WHAT WE HAVE HERE.

03:04.227 --> 03:05.837
YOU THINK
THIS IS TERRORISTS?

03:05.837 --> 03:07.535
WELL, WE CAN'T RULE IT OUT.WELL, I THINK WE CAN.

03:07.535 --> 03:09.058
SOMEONE JUST WANTED
THE DEAD GUY DEAD.

03:09.058 --> 03:10.625
AND WHY DO YOU THINK THAT?

03:10.625 --> 03:12.888
BECAUSE HE'S DEAD.
I MEAN, LOOK AT THIS PLACE.

03:12.888 --> 03:15.195
BOMBER COULD OF KILLED
A DOZEN PEOPLE IF HE WANTED TO.

03:15.195 --> 03:17.371
BUT, NOPE, THIS GUY
JUST BUMPED OFF ONE.

03:17.371 --> 03:19.373
PRETTY INEFFECTIVE TERRORISM,
IF YOU ASK ME.

03:19.373 --> 03:21.244
WOULD BE A GOOD WAY
TO BURY A HOMICIDE.

03:21.244 --> 03:23.028
NONETHELESS,
WE ARE GONNA LOOK AT THIS

03:23.028 --> 03:25.248
AS A POSSIBLE
TERRORIST ATTACK

03:25.248 --> 03:27.163
UNTIL WE HAVE
CONCLUSIVE EVIDENCE

03:27.163 --> 03:29.426
THAT SHOWS US
SOMETHING ELSE, OKAY?

03:29.426 --> 03:31.515
CALL THE NSA AND SEE
IF THEY HEARD ANY CHATTER

03:31.515 --> 03:32.647
ABOUT AN ATTACK, OKAY?

03:32.647 --> 03:34.214
SIR, WE FOUND PIECES
FROM THE CASE

03:34.214 --> 03:35.867
THE CHARGE WAS IN
WHEN IT EXPLODED.

03:35.867 --> 03:37.869
WE ALSO FOUND THIS.

03:37.869 --> 03:39.871
A BIT STRANGE, ACTUALLY.

03:39.871 --> 03:41.569
WHAT IS IT?IT'S BLANKETING MATERIAL.

03:41.569 --> 03:44.006
IT APPEARS TO HAVE BEEN PLACED
ABOVE AND BENEATH THE CHARGE.

03:44.006 --> 03:45.573
AND WHY'S THAT STRANGE?

03:45.573 --> 03:47.096
IT WOULD HAVE DAMPENED
THE EXPLOSION.

03:47.096 --> 03:48.576
USUALLY, A BOMBER
WANTS A BIGGER BOOM, YOU KNOW?

03:48.576 --> 03:50.360
NOT THIS ONE.

03:50.360 --> 03:52.319
THIS DEVICE WAS DESIGNED
TO BE LETHAL ONLY TO SOMEONE

03:52.319 --> 03:53.755
SITUATED
RIGHT NEXT TO IT.

03:53.755 --> 03:56.148
I NEVER SAW THAT BEFORE.

03:57.889 --> 03:59.804
DEAD GUY.

04:00.631 --> 04:03.025
BOOM.

04:03.025 --> 04:06.071
♪♪♪

