04:16.430 --> 04:18.301
Male voice: IT'S 9:00.

04:18.301 --> 04:21.783
DID YOU JUST TELL ME
WHAT TIME IT IS?

04:21.783 --> 04:24.612
EXCUSE ME?

04:24.612 --> 04:25.961
SOMEONE JUST SAID
THE TIME.

04:25.961 --> 04:27.267
OH.
YEAH, MY COMPUTER.

04:27.267 --> 04:29.094
IT'S 9:00.

04:29.094 --> 04:31.183
I'VE PROGRAMMED IT TO ANNOUNCE
THE TIME EVERY QUARTER-HOUR.

04:31.183 --> 04:32.794
I THINK IT MAKES ME
MORE EFFICIENT.

04:32.794 --> 04:35.492
A REGULAR REMINDER
OF THE PASSAGE OF TIME

04:35.492 --> 04:37.668
SEEMS TO HAVE A SUBTLE
BUT DEFINITE...

04:37.668 --> 04:39.104
I'LL TURN
THE VOLUME DOWN.

04:39.104 --> 04:40.236
THANK YOU.

04:40.236 --> 04:42.107
[ FIRE ALARM BLARING ]

04:42.107 --> 04:43.457
IT'S NOT ME.

04:43.457 --> 04:45.285
THEY'RE TESTING
THE FIRE-ALARM SYSTEM.

04:45.285 --> 04:47.548
THEY'LL BE WORKING ON IT
FOR THE NEXT COUPLE DAYS.

04:47.548 --> 04:48.723
[ FIRE ALARM BLARING ]GREAT!

04:52.944 --> 04:56.513
WE GOT AN I.D. ON THE GUY
WHO WAS KILLED BY THE BOMB.

04:56.513 --> 04:58.950
DAVID RONALDO, 47 YEARS OLD,
FROM HILLSBORO.

04:58.950 --> 05:01.083
HIS FAMILY THERE'S
BEEN NOTIFIED.

05:01.083 --> 05:03.651
DOES IT CONFIRM JANE'S IDEA
THAT HE WAS THE ORIGINAL TARGET?

05:03.651 --> 05:06.001
TURNS OUT HE'S CONNECTED
TO AN OLD MURDER.

05:06.001 --> 05:10.658
14 YEARS AGO, A WOMAN WAS KILLED
BY A GUY NAMED LUIS CRUZ.

05:10.658 --> 05:13.095
HE BUSTED INTO HER HOUSE
AND SHOT HER.

05:13.095 --> 05:15.010
HE'S BEEN ON DEATH ROW
FOR THE PAST 11 YEARS.

05:15.010 --> 05:16.577
HOW'S RONALDO CONNECTED?

05:16.577 --> 05:18.796
FOR SOME REASON, RONALDO THOUGHT
CRUZ WAS INNOCENT.

05:18.796 --> 05:20.668
HE'S BEEN TRYING
TO GET HIM EXONERATED.

05:20.668 --> 05:22.974
HOW DOES THAT GET YOU KILLED?YOU GOT ME.

05:22.974 --> 05:24.585
ABBOTT'S GONE DOWN TO

05:24.585 --> 05:26.151
THE WEST LIVINGSTON
DEATH ROW UNIT TO TALK TO CRUZ,

05:26.151 --> 05:28.197
SEE IF HE CAN SHED SOME LIGHT
ON THE SITUATION.

05:28.197 --> 05:30.112
HE LEFT ALREADY?
WHAT'S THE HURRY?

05:30.112 --> 05:32.332
CRUZ IS SENTENCED TO BE EXECUTED
IN THREE DAYS.

05:40.122 --> 05:41.689
NO, NOT DAVID.

05:43.734 --> 05:46.215
I'M AFRAID SO, MR. CRUZ.

05:48.391 --> 05:50.828
IT AIN'T RIGHT.
T-THERE'S NO SENSE TO IT.

05:50.828 --> 05:52.700
HOW DID YOU KNOW
MR. RONALDO?

05:52.700 --> 05:56.704
WE, UH...
WE GREW UP TOGETHER.

05:56.704 --> 05:59.707
HIS FOLKS WERE
MY -- MY FOSTER PARENTS

05:59.707 --> 06:01.883
FROM THE TIME I WAS 8.

06:01.883 --> 06:06.061
DAVID AND ME,
WE WERE BROTHERS, TIGHT.

06:06.061 --> 06:10.587
I SHOULD'VE BEEN MORE LIKE HIM,
LIKE DAVID.

06:10.587 --> 06:15.244
HE WAS A GOOD STUDENT,
GOOD SON, GOOD BROTHER.

06:15.244 --> 06:18.247
BUT I WAS --
I WAS A MESS.

06:18.247 --> 06:21.293
FIRST NARCOTICS ARREST
WAS AT THE AGE OF 16, RIGHT?

06:21.293 --> 06:22.904
DAVID WOULD BAIL ME OUT,

06:22.904 --> 06:25.080
HELP ME GET INTO A PROGRAM
OR WHATEVER.

06:25.080 --> 06:29.084
THEN I'D SCREW THINGS UP
AND BACK I'D GO.

06:29.084 --> 06:31.782
RECENTLY, HE WAS TRYING TO GET
YOUR CONVICTION OVERTURNED.

06:31.782 --> 06:35.046
HE'D BEEN WORKING WITH MY --
WITH MY LAWYER FOR YEARS,

06:35.046 --> 06:38.441
SPENDING HIS OWN MONEY,
TRACKING DOWN ANY --

06:38.441 --> 06:41.618
ANY CRAZY THING
THAT MIGHT HELP AN APPEAL.

06:41.618 --> 06:45.753
MR. CRUZ, HAVE YOU HEARD
FROM HIM RECENTLY?

06:45.753 --> 06:48.103
I GOT A MESSAGE
A FEW DAYS AGO

06:48.103 --> 06:51.106
SAYING THAT HE -- HE MIGHT HAVE
SOME GOOD NEWS,

06:51.106 --> 06:53.587
BUT HE DIDN'T WANT TO SAY
UNTIL HE WAS SURE.

06:53.587 --> 06:55.719
AND HE NEVER MENTIONED
WHAT IT WAS?

06:55.719 --> 06:57.199
NO.

06:57.199 --> 06:59.375
YOU HAVE ANY IDEA
OF PROBLEMS HE MAY HAVE HAD?

06:59.375 --> 07:02.117
GIRLFRIEND PROBLEMS,
MONEY ISSUES?

07:02.117 --> 07:03.771
NEVER MENTIONED ANY.

07:03.771 --> 07:06.774
I APPRECIATE YOUR TIME.

07:06.774 --> 07:07.862
[ TAPS ON GLASS ]

07:13.607 --> 07:17.175
AGENT, I DIDN'T KILL
THAT WOMAN.

07:18.916 --> 07:21.484
I DON'T EXPECT YOU
TO DO ANYTHING.

07:21.484 --> 07:24.922
I JUST NEED SOMEBODY
TO BELIEVE ME.

07:26.968 --> 07:30.145
ALL THE THINGS
I'VE DONE IN MY LIFE,

07:30.145 --> 07:32.060
I NEVER KILLED ANYBODY.

07:32.060 --> 07:35.542
I'D APPRECIATE IT
IF YOU'D JUST --

07:35.542 --> 07:37.457
JUST TRY TO BELIEVE THAT.

07:43.898 --> 07:45.116
THANKS.

07:54.778 --> 07:56.737
WHAT HAVE WE GOT, KIDS?

07:56.737 --> 07:58.086
FOUND AN ATM
WITH A CAMERA

07:58.086 --> 07:59.870
ACROSS THE STREET
FROM THE EXPLOSION.

07:59.870 --> 08:02.003
THERE'S NO VIDEO,
BUT IT AUTOMATICALLY TAKES

08:02.003 --> 08:04.701
A STILL PICTURE
EVERY SECOND, SO...

08:04.701 --> 08:08.400
THAT'S ABOUT A MINUTE AND A HALF
BEFORE IT HAPPENED.

08:08.400 --> 08:11.708
THEN ABOUT 20 SECONDS LATER,
OUR BOMBER APPEARS.

08:11.708 --> 08:14.145
TECHS CONFIRMED THAT'S
THE BRIEFCASE THE BOMB WAS IN.

08:14.145 --> 08:16.104
CAN YOU ENHANCE THE IMAGE?I ALREADY DID,

08:16.104 --> 08:18.106
BUT THE DISGUISE MAKES HIM
IMPOSSIBLE TO IDENTIFY.

08:18.106 --> 08:19.673
FACIAL RECOGNITION
CAN'T DO ANYTHING.

08:19.673 --> 08:22.153
THAT'S QUITE THE RUG.

08:22.153 --> 08:24.591
THEN THE MOM AND BABY
APPEAR...

08:26.027 --> 08:28.986
THE BUS PULLS IN,
BUS PULLS OUT,

08:28.986 --> 08:30.597
AND...

08:30.597 --> 08:31.989
BOOM!

08:31.989 --> 08:33.425
WHOA, WHOA.

08:33.425 --> 08:35.340
OKAY, CAN YOU BACK IT UP
A WAYS?

08:35.340 --> 08:36.777
BEFORE THE BUS PULLS IN?

08:39.562 --> 08:40.955
THE BRIEFCASES --
THEY'RE IDENTICAL.

08:40.955 --> 08:42.434
CAN YOU ENLARGE THAT?

08:42.434 --> 08:43.958
[ BEEP ]

08:43.958 --> 08:46.569
SEE, I-I DON'T THINK
THAT'S A COINCIDENCE.

08:46.569 --> 08:48.615
OKAY, CAN -- CAN YOU PULL UP
AN IMAGE

08:48.615 --> 08:51.661
BEFORE THE EXPLOSION
BUT AFTER THE BUS PULLED IN?

08:52.532 --> 08:54.708
THERE'S ONLY
ONE BRIEFCASE NOW,

08:54.708 --> 08:57.362
SO THE BOMBER
MUST HAVE TAKEN RONALDO'S.

08:57.362 --> 08:59.930
LEAVING RONALDO
WITH THE BOMB AT HIS FEET.

08:59.930 --> 09:02.237
SO, THE BOMBER
NOT ONLY WANTED RONALDO DEAD,

09:02.237 --> 09:04.021
HE WANTED
WHAT WAS IN THAT BRIEFCASE.

09:04.021 --> 09:05.457
EXACTLY.

09:05.457 --> 09:07.242
LOOK AT THAT WOMAN.

09:07.242 --> 09:09.374
CAN -- CAN YOU BACK HER UP
A BIT?

09:09.374 --> 09:11.246
YOU SEE?

09:11.246 --> 09:13.509
SHE'S THERE ON PURPOSE
TO DISTRACT RONALDO

09:13.509 --> 09:14.902
FROM THE BRIEFCASE.

09:14.902 --> 09:16.686
YOU FIND THAT WOMAN,
YOU WILL FIND YOUR BOMBER.

09:19.036 --> 09:21.256
TRY FACIAL RECOGNITION.

09:37.446 --> 09:39.753
GINA PETROCELLI, OPEN UP!

09:39.753 --> 09:41.929
MS. PETROCELLI!

09:41.929 --> 09:43.191
Gina: YES?

09:43.191 --> 09:45.236
FBI.
OPEN THE DOOR.OKAY.

09:45.236 --> 09:47.717
I JUST GOT OUT OF THE SHOWER.
I NEED A MINUTE.

09:47.717 --> 09:49.719
YOU HAVE 30 SECONDS.

09:49.719 --> 09:52.069
NO PROBLEM.
JUST NEED TO DRY OFF.

09:52.069 --> 09:54.071
WHAT'S THIS ABOUT,
ANYWAY?

09:54.071 --> 09:56.639
20 SECONDS AND WE'RE COMING IN,
MS. PETROCELLI.

09:56.639 --> 09:59.599
OKAY, JUST...
DON'T SHOOT OR ANYTHING.

09:59.599 --> 10:01.252
JUST NEED TO PUT
SOME PANTS ON.

10:01.252 --> 10:03.211
THOSE PANTS
LOOK ALL RIGHT TO ME, GINA.

10:06.127 --> 10:08.129
[ DOLL CRIES ]

10:08.129 --> 10:10.131
THIS YOUR BABY?

10:10.131 --> 10:11.175
YEAH.

10:11.175 --> 10:12.437
CUTE.

10:15.136 --> 10:17.355
GINA, YOU'VE HAD RUN-INS
WITH THE LAW BEFORE --

10:17.355 --> 10:18.835
ARRESTS FOR FRAUD.

10:18.835 --> 10:22.317
I THINK YOU KNOW
THIS IS FAR WORSE THAN THAT.

10:22.317 --> 10:24.275
I DIDN'T KNOW ANYTHING
ABOUT THE BOMB.

10:24.275 --> 10:25.450
I SWEAR.

10:25.450 --> 10:28.671
NO IDEA
THAT WAS GONNA HAPPEN.

10:28.671 --> 10:30.891
YOU KNOW WHO THIS IS?

10:30.891 --> 10:32.588
YES. ABSOLUTELY.

10:32.588 --> 10:35.504
HIS NAME IS PETER KOCH.
HE'S A PRIVATE INVESTIGATOR.

10:35.504 --> 10:37.158
I HELP HIM OUT
SOMETIMES.

10:37.158 --> 10:38.768
I'LL HAVE WYLIE
RUN HIM.

10:38.768 --> 10:40.422
WHAT DO YOU MEAN
"HELP HIM OUT"?

10:40.422 --> 10:42.990
WHEN THERE'S SOMETHING
HE NEEDS TO GET...CREATIVELY.

10:42.990 --> 10:44.208
YOU MEAN ILLEGALLY.

10:44.208 --> 10:45.993
WHATEVER.

10:45.993 --> 10:48.691
PETE THROWS ME SOME MONEY.
I DO WHAT HE ASKS ME TO DO.

10:48.691 --> 10:50.432
WHY DID HE KILL
DAVID RONALDO?

10:50.432 --> 10:52.260
I DON'T KNOW ANYTHING
ABOUT THAT.

10:52.260 --> 10:55.002
ALL PETE TOLD ME IS HE NEEDED
HELP SNATCHING A BRIEFCASE.

10:55.002 --> 10:56.917
I DISTRACT THE MARK.
HE MAKES THE GRAB.

10:56.917 --> 10:58.614
EASY.

10:58.614 --> 11:00.137
THEN I'M WALKING AWAY,
AND -- BOOM --

11:00.137 --> 11:02.357
I'M FACEDOWN ON THE SIDEWALK,
I CAN'T HEAR,

11:02.357 --> 11:04.446
PEOPLE AROUND ME
ARE BLEEDING.

11:04.446 --> 11:07.362
YOU THINK I WOULD GET INTO THAT
ON PURPOSE?

11:07.362 --> 11:09.320
HE DIDN'T TELL YOU
ANYTHING ABOUT IT?

11:09.320 --> 11:11.192
[ SIGHS ] NO.

11:11.192 --> 11:14.935
JUST, UH...
THAT IT WAS A BIG JOB.

11:14.935 --> 11:17.198
HE WAS GONNA MAKE
A LOT OF MONEY.

11:17.198 --> 11:20.505
NEW DEVELOPMENT.
PETE KOCH IS DEAD.

11:23.378 --> 11:26.424
LOCAL P.D. FOUND KOCH'S BODY
IN AN ALLEY IN EAST AUSTIN

11:26.424 --> 11:28.992
ABOUT FOUR HOURS AGO --
GUNSHOT TO THE HEAD.

11:28.992 --> 11:30.777
HIS WATCH AND WALLET
WERE MISSING,

11:30.777 --> 11:32.866
SO THEY ASSUMED
IT WAS A ROBBERY GONE BAD.

11:32.866 --> 11:34.345
ANY SIGNS
OF THE BRIEFCASE?

11:34.345 --> 11:36.391
NONE. AND WE HAD
HIS APARTMENT SEARCHED.

11:36.391 --> 11:37.566
IT WASN'T THERE, EITHER.

11:37.566 --> 11:39.220
I'D SAY
THAT RULES OUT ROBBERY.

11:39.220 --> 11:40.700
WHAT ABOUT
GINA PETROCELLI?

11:40.700 --> 11:43.703
THIS ONE,
I THINK SHE'S TELLING THE TRUTH.

11:43.703 --> 11:45.661
SHE DIDN'T KNOW ABOUT THE BOMB,
AND SHE DOESN'T KNOW

11:45.661 --> 11:47.054
WHO HIRED KOCH
TO GET THE BRIEFCASE.

11:47.054 --> 11:48.359
OKAY.

11:48.359 --> 11:49.709
CHARGE PETROCELLI
WITH CONSPIRACY

11:49.709 --> 11:51.623
AND WHATEVER ELSE
YOU CAN THINK OF.

11:51.623 --> 11:52.537
ANYTHING ELSE?

11:52.537 --> 11:54.714
NO, THAT'S IT.

11:56.803 --> 11:59.327
JANE.

12:02.591 --> 12:04.419
DO YOU KNOW
WHAT THIS IS?

12:04.419 --> 12:06.073
I'M BETTING
IT'S A TRANSCRIPT

12:06.073 --> 12:07.988
FROM LUIS CRUZ'S TRIAL
FOR MURDER.

12:07.988 --> 12:08.989
GOOD READ?

12:08.989 --> 12:10.817
IT'S A LITTLE DRY.

12:10.817 --> 12:12.383
CRUZ WAS A DRUG ADDICT.

12:12.383 --> 12:13.907
THE NIGHT OF THE MURDER,

12:13.907 --> 12:15.735
HE SAID
THAT HE WAS ALONE, USING.

12:15.735 --> 12:17.737
NO ONE TO CONFIRM IT.

12:17.737 --> 12:19.826
THE D.A.
HAD CIRCUMSTANTIAL EVIDENCE

12:19.826 --> 12:21.610
AND A PIECE
OF LUIS' CLOTHING

12:21.610 --> 12:23.481
WITH THE DEAD WOMAN'S
BLOOD ON IT.

12:23.481 --> 12:24.874
THE BLOOD CLINCHED IT.

12:24.874 --> 12:27.181
YES, WELL,
BLOOD'S VERY EASY TO PLANT.

12:27.181 --> 12:29.444
CHILDISHLY EASY, REALLY.YES, IT IS.

12:29.444 --> 12:31.576
YOU DON'T THINK CRUZ DID IT?
WHY?

12:31.576 --> 12:34.797
WELL, IT'S JUST A FEELING
THAT I CAN'T SHAKE.

12:34.797 --> 12:36.581
WHAT DO YOU THINK?

12:36.581 --> 12:40.150
WELL, DAVID RONALDO WAS LOOKING
FOR EVIDENCE TO CLEAR CRUZ.

12:40.150 --> 12:43.066
HE WAS KILLED AND HAD
SOMETHING STOLEN FROM HIM.

12:43.066 --> 12:46.461
THAT PRETTY STRONGLY SUGGESTS
THAT HE WAS ONTO SOMETHING.

12:46.461 --> 12:48.855
WHICH MEANS THAT,
IN THE NEXT FEW DAYS,

12:48.855 --> 12:51.901
THE STATE OF TEXAS IS GOING
TO EXECUTE AN INNOCENT MAN.

12:51.901 --> 12:53.598
AND ONCE HE'S DEAD,

12:53.598 --> 12:56.950
THERE'S VERY LITTLE INCENTIVE
TO REOPEN THE CASE...

12:56.950 --> 12:58.952
WHICH
THE REAL KILLER KNOWS.

12:58.952 --> 13:02.738
SO...

13:02.738 --> 13:05.175
WHAT ARE WE GONNA DO
ABOUT ALL THIS?

13:05.175 --> 13:07.308
OH, WELL, I THINK I CAN COME UP
WITH SOMETHING.

13:07.308 --> 13:08.613
[ CHUCKLES ]

13:13.836 --> 13:15.838
14 YEARS AGO, LUIS CRUZ
WAS ACCUSED OF MURDERING

13:15.838 --> 13:18.058
THIS WOMAN --
SARAH FEINBERG.

13:18.058 --> 13:19.711
SHE WAS SHOT TO DEATH
IN HER HOME,

13:19.711 --> 13:21.452
APPARENTLY BY AN INTRUDER.

13:21.452 --> 13:24.847
HER BODY WAS FOUND
BY HER HUSBAND, EDWARD FEINBERG.

13:24.847 --> 13:27.154
EDWARD WAS A PSYCHIATRIST

13:27.154 --> 13:29.330
AT THE UNIVERSITY
TEACHING HOSPITAL.

13:29.330 --> 13:31.549
HE FOUND HIS WIFE'S BODY
WHEN HE ARRIVED HOME

13:31.549 --> 13:32.986
LATER THAT NIGHT.

13:32.986 --> 13:34.639
ANYTHING CONNECTING CRUZ
TO THE FEINBERGS?

13:34.639 --> 13:36.206
YES.

13:36.206 --> 13:37.686
EDWARD FEINBERG KNEW CRUZ

13:37.686 --> 13:39.993
FROM A HALFWAY-HOUSE
DRUG-TREATMENT PROGRAM

13:39.993 --> 13:41.211
THAT FEINBERG RAN.

13:41.211 --> 13:43.823
CRUZ AND FEINBERG
HAD AN ARGUMENT

13:43.823 --> 13:46.347
BECAUSE CRUZ SHOWED UP
TO A THERAPY SESSION HIGH

13:46.347 --> 13:47.696
THREE DAYS
BEFORE THE MURDER.

13:47.696 --> 13:49.002
AND THE D.A. CLAIMED

13:49.002 --> 13:50.786
THAT THAT MADE CRUZ
KILL SARAH FEINBERG?

13:50.786 --> 13:51.918
THAT'S THIN.

13:51.918 --> 13:53.484
WHAT PUT CRUZ
AT THE MURDER SCENE?

13:53.484 --> 13:54.964
THEY FOUND
A SWEATSHIRT OF CRUZ'S

13:54.964 --> 13:56.574
SNAGGED ON A BUSH
OUTSIDE OF THE HOUSE

13:56.574 --> 13:58.185
WITH SARAH FEINBERG'S BLOOD
ON IT.

13:58.185 --> 14:00.404
THERE WAS ALSO GUNPOWDER
ON ONE SLEEVE.

14:00.404 --> 14:01.231
WHAT ABOUT THE GUN?

14:01.231 --> 14:02.319
THEY DIDN'T FIND IT.

14:02.319 --> 14:04.408
IT'S 10:00.

14:04.408 --> 14:05.757
I'LL TURN IT OFF.

14:05.757 --> 14:07.194
NO WORRIES.
IT'S GOOD TO KNOW.

14:07.194 --> 14:08.673
Patrick: 10:00.

14:08.673 --> 14:11.328
WE BELIEVE
THAT DAVID RONALDO WAS MURDERED

14:11.328 --> 14:14.766
BECAUSE HE HAD EVIDENCE
THAT WOULD CLEAR LUIS CRUZ.

14:14.766 --> 14:16.681
WE NEED TO FIND OUT
WHAT THAT WAS.

14:16.681 --> 14:19.206
AND BECAUSE THEY'RE GOING
TO EXECUTE CRUZ

14:19.206 --> 14:23.166
IN ABOUT...50 HOURS,
WE SHOULD HURRY UP.

14:23.166 --> 14:25.952
BOSS,
IS THERE ANY EVIDENCE

14:25.952 --> 14:28.389
THAT THE COPS OR THE PROSECUTORS
MADE A MISTAKE?

14:28.389 --> 14:29.869
NOT THAT I CAN POINT TO.

14:29.869 --> 14:31.740
AND THIS CASE
WAS FULLY APPEALED, RIGHT?

14:31.740 --> 14:33.133
YES.

14:33.133 --> 14:35.613
THEN CAN I ASK
WHY WE'RE TAKING THIS ON?

14:35.613 --> 14:37.920
I-I DON'T WANT TO SOUND COLD,
BUT IT SEEMS TO ME

14:37.920 --> 14:39.966
THAT THE SYSTEM DID
WHAT IT WAS SUPPOSED TO DO.

14:39.966 --> 14:41.445
Patrick:
NO, IT DIDN'T.

14:41.445 --> 14:43.447
BECAUSE LUIS CRUZ
IS INNOCENT.

14:43.447 --> 14:44.796
YOU'RE ABSOLUTELY CERTAIN
OF THAT?

14:44.796 --> 14:46.581
WELL, I'M NOT ABSOLUTELY CERTAIN
OF ANYTHING.

14:46.581 --> 14:49.279
BUT I'M CONFIDENT ENOUGH TO KNOW
THAT I'D LIKE TO TRY AND HELP.

14:49.279 --> 14:50.977
THAT'S GOOD ENOUGH
FOR ME.

14:50.977 --> 14:52.108
ME TOO.

14:52.108 --> 14:55.764
OKAY.
LET'S DO IT.

14:55.764 --> 14:57.635
FISCHER, CHO, WORK RONALDO.

14:57.635 --> 14:59.724
GO TO HIS APARTMENT,
SEE IF YOU CAN FIND ANYTHING.

14:59.724 --> 15:00.856
I'LL CALL
THE GOVERNOR'S OFFICE

15:00.856 --> 15:02.771
AND LET HIM KNOW
WHAT WE'RE UP TO.

15:02.771 --> 15:04.773
JANE, LISBON,
TALK TO THE FEINBERGS.

15:04.773 --> 15:06.340
WYLIE...

15:09.560 --> 15:13.086
...JUST KEEP LETTING US KNOW
WHAT TIME IT IS.

15:14.652 --> 15:16.350
UH-HUH.
REALLY?

15:16.350 --> 15:19.396
WELL, WE'RE JUST --
JUST GETTING HERE NOW.

15:19.396 --> 15:22.312
I CAN'T DO ANYTHING
TONIGHT.

15:22.312 --> 15:25.272
THIS CASE
COULD GO ALL HOURS.

15:25.272 --> 15:26.969
THURSDAY'S GREAT.

15:26.969 --> 15:28.405
OKAY. ME TOO.

15:28.405 --> 15:29.711
BYE, MARCUS.

15:29.711 --> 15:31.408
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

15:34.368 --> 15:35.847
WHAT?

15:35.847 --> 15:38.154
NOTHING. NOTHING.

15:38.154 --> 15:39.677
MR. FEINBERG?

15:39.677 --> 15:40.852
YES.

15:40.852 --> 15:42.767
YOU'RE FROM THE FBI?

15:42.767 --> 15:46.162
YES, I'M AGENT LISBON.
THIS IS PATRICK JANE.

15:46.162 --> 15:47.250
COME IN.

15:57.913 --> 15:59.523
THIS IS MY WIFE, MAE.

15:59.523 --> 16:00.785
NICE TO MEET YOU.

16:00.785 --> 16:02.439
SIT, PLEASE, SIT.

16:06.487 --> 16:08.010
NOW...

16:08.010 --> 16:10.056
[CLEARS THROAT]
WHAT EXACTLY ARE YOU HERE FOR?

16:10.056 --> 16:12.449
YOU SAID ON THE PHONE
IT HAD TO DO WITH LUIS CRUZ.

16:12.449 --> 16:14.538
YES. HIS FRIEND
DAVID RONALDO WAS KILLED.

16:14.538 --> 16:16.018
HAVE YOU EVER
HEARD OF HIM?

16:16.018 --> 16:18.238
I DON'T THINK SO.
NO.

16:18.238 --> 16:21.850
UM, AND WHAT DOES HIS DEATH
HAVE TO DO WITH US?

16:21.850 --> 16:24.287
IT'S COMPLICATED.

16:24.287 --> 16:26.420
WELL, THAT'S --

16:26.420 --> 16:28.378
THAT'S A LITTLE EVASIVE,
NOW, ISN'T IT?

16:28.378 --> 16:30.554
THIS IS AN ONGOING
INVESTIGATION.

16:30.554 --> 16:32.556
I'M NOT ALLOWED
TO SAY MORE.

16:32.556 --> 16:35.951
UH, THIS IS THE ROOM WHERE
YOUR WIFE WAS KILLED, RIGHT?

16:35.951 --> 16:37.344
YES.

16:37.344 --> 16:39.041
YOU HAVE
AN OFFICE HERE, TOO.

16:39.041 --> 16:40.651
YES, I SEE PATIENTS HERE.

16:40.651 --> 16:42.218
THAT MUST BE
KIND OF WEIRD.

16:42.218 --> 16:44.612
YOU LIKE TO PROVOKE,
NOW, DON'T YOU?

16:44.612 --> 16:46.266
CLASSIC DEFENSE MECHANISM.

16:46.266 --> 16:50.705
AND, YES, IT WAS,
AS YOU SAY, "WEIRD"

16:50.705 --> 16:52.576
FOR SOME TIME.

16:52.576 --> 16:55.231
BUT I WASN'T GOING
TO LET CRUZ

16:55.231 --> 16:57.103
CHASE ME
OUT OF MY OWN HOME.

16:57.103 --> 16:59.322
WELL, I'M NOT JUDGING, HONESTLY.
I'M JUST CURIOUS.

16:59.322 --> 17:01.890
AND I MUST SAY, I LOVE WHAT
YOU'VE DONE WITH THE REMODELING.

17:01.890 --> 17:03.326
OH,
WE DID IT TOGETHER.

17:03.326 --> 17:04.588
I DETECTED YOUR TOUCH.

17:04.588 --> 17:05.894
HOW LONG HAVE YOU TWO
BEEN MARRIED?

17:05.894 --> 17:09.941
OH, ALMOST 11 YEARS.

17:09.941 --> 17:12.596
AND DID YOU KNOW EACH OTHER
AT THE TIME OF THE MURDER?

17:12.596 --> 17:15.295
NO. I WAS A NEW
GRADUATE STUDENT THEN.

17:15.295 --> 17:17.862
EDWARD WAS FAR TOO IMPORTANT
TO NOTICE ME.

17:17.862 --> 17:19.299
[ CHUCKLES ]

17:19.299 --> 17:23.303
I WENT THROUGH
A PERIOD OF DEEP GRIEVING

17:23.303 --> 17:25.783
FOR SEVERAL YEARS
AFTER SARAH WAS KILLED.

17:25.783 --> 17:28.395
BUT I PULLED MYSELF
OUT OF IT,

17:28.395 --> 17:31.920
AND WE WERE FORTUNATE ENOUGH
TO, UH...FIND EACH OTHER.

17:31.920 --> 17:33.791
SO, IT WAS FATE, HUH?
WONDERFUL.

17:33.791 --> 17:35.880
A COUPLE MORE QUESTIONS
BEFORE WE GO.

17:35.880 --> 17:37.752
HAVE YOU EVER CONSIDERED
SUICIDE?

17:37.752 --> 17:39.928
NO.

17:39.928 --> 17:41.712
AND YOU, MAE --

17:41.712 --> 17:43.584
DID YOUR FATHER GO TO YOUR
HIGH-SCHOOL GRADUATION CEREMONY?

17:43.584 --> 17:45.455
NO.

17:45.455 --> 17:47.544
WHAT DOES THAT HAVE TO DO
WITH ANYTHING?

17:47.544 --> 17:49.633
YOU'D BE SURPRISED.
THANK YOU FOR YOUR TIME.

17:49.633 --> 17:51.331
BEFORE WE GO,
DO YOU THINK I COULD

17:51.331 --> 17:52.897
JUST QUICKLY USE
YOUR BATHROOM?

17:52.897 --> 17:54.377
YEAH, OF COURSE.

17:54.377 --> 17:55.857
IT'S THROUGH THE KITCHEN,
ON YOUR RIGHT.

17:55.857 --> 17:57.641
THANK YOU.

18:37.638 --> 18:40.206
ONE LAST QUESTION.
JUST CURIOUS --

18:40.206 --> 18:42.121
HOW LONG BEFORE
THE FIRST MRS. FEINBERG DIED

18:42.121 --> 18:44.340
DID YOU START YOUR AFFAIR?

18:44.340 --> 18:46.995
FASCINATING METHOD
YOU HAVE,

18:46.995 --> 18:48.866
IF IT IS A METHOD.

18:48.866 --> 18:52.043
MAE AND I DID NOT HAVE
AN AFFAIR BEFORE MY WIFE DIED.

18:52.043 --> 18:54.045
REALLY?
YOU'RE SO CAREFUL TO MENTION

18:54.045 --> 18:57.745
YOUR "DEEP GRIEVING PERIOD,"
EVEN NOW.

18:57.745 --> 18:59.921
AND, YOU KNOW, THIS IS NOT
REALLY THE HOUSE OF SOMEONE

18:59.921 --> 19:01.705
THAT'S SENTIMENTAL --
QUITE THE OPPOSITE.

19:01.705 --> 19:04.317
YOU'RE VERY OBSERVANT,
MR. JANE.

19:04.317 --> 19:06.188
AND PERHAPS YOU'RE RIGHT.

19:06.188 --> 19:08.190
I DO PROTEST TOO MUCH.

19:08.190 --> 19:11.237
BUT I HAVE GROWN WEARY
AND DEFENSIVE ON THE SUBJECT,

19:11.237 --> 19:13.152
AS I'M SURE
YOU MIGHT UNDERSTAND.

19:13.152 --> 19:15.023
I DO, I DO.

19:15.023 --> 19:16.677
I UNDERSTAND THAT LUIS CRUZ
DIDN'T KILL YOUR WIFE. YOU DID.

19:16.677 --> 19:19.680
AND WE'RE GONNA PROVE IT.

19:19.680 --> 19:22.204
UNLESS YOU WANT TO CONFESS NOW
AND SAVE US ALL SOME TIME.

19:22.204 --> 19:23.640
NOW, I ASSUMED
THAT THIS WAS WHERE

19:23.640 --> 19:25.033
THIS WAS
ALL BUILDING TOWARD.

19:25.033 --> 19:26.469
YOU'RE NOT THE FIRST
TO THINK IT.

19:26.469 --> 19:28.297
I WAS HER HUSBAND,
AFTER ALL.

19:28.297 --> 19:29.472
BUT IT'S NOT TRUE.

19:29.472 --> 19:31.648
LEAVE MY HUSBAND ALONE.

19:32.867 --> 19:34.260
I'D LIKE YOU BOTH
TO LEAVE NOW.

19:34.260 --> 19:35.652
NOW.
YES.
OF COURSE, MA'AM.

19:35.652 --> 19:36.827
YES. JANE?

19:43.921 --> 19:47.403
RONALDO DID NOT HAVE
MUCH OF A LIFE

19:47.403 --> 19:49.492
OUTSIDE THE CRUZ CASE.

19:49.492 --> 19:50.450
GUESS NOT.

19:50.450 --> 19:52.191
THIS IS WEIRD.WHAT?

19:52.191 --> 19:55.542
EVERYTHING TAPED TO THE WALLS
IS OLD EXCEPT FOR THIS MAP.

19:55.542 --> 19:58.806
LOOKS BRAND-NEW.
WHAT'S IT DOING HERE?

19:58.806 --> 20:00.590
GOT ME.

20:00.590 --> 20:02.810
LET'S MAKE SURE
WE TAKE IT BACK WITH US.

20:04.899 --> 20:07.771
HEY, DID LISBON
DATE ON THE JOB AT CBI?

20:07.771 --> 20:09.382
DON'T KNOW.
NEVER ASKED.

20:09.382 --> 20:12.167
SURPRISING TO SEE HER AND PIKE
HOOK UP, HUH?

20:12.167 --> 20:14.517
WOULDN'T HAVE PUT THOSE TWO
TOGETHER.

20:15.953 --> 20:18.608
YOU EVER WONDER
WHAT JANE THINKS ABOUT IT?

20:18.608 --> 20:20.697
NEVER.
REALLY? WHY NOT?

20:20.697 --> 20:21.959
MY BRAIN WOULD EXPLODE.

20:33.144 --> 20:34.798
HEY, CHO.

20:34.798 --> 20:37.279
DOES RONALDO SEEM LIKE THE TYPE
WHO'D GO DIVING?

20:39.803 --> 20:42.458
RONALDO STARTED TAKING DIVING
LESSONS ABOUT A MONTH AGO.

20:42.458 --> 20:43.807
DIVING LESSONS?
WHY?

20:43.807 --> 20:46.027
WAS HE PLANNING ON GOING
TO THE OCEAN?

20:46.027 --> 20:47.463
UH,
NOT THAT WE COULD TELL.

20:47.463 --> 20:48.812
WELL, ISN'T IT OBVIOUS?

20:48.812 --> 20:50.292
HE WAS LOOKING
FOR THE GUN.

20:50.292 --> 20:52.163
HE WAS?SURE.

20:52.163 --> 20:53.991
WELL, THE POLICE
STILL HAVEN'T FOUND THE GUN

20:53.991 --> 20:55.384
THAT KILLED SARAH FEINBERG.

20:55.384 --> 20:56.777
THIS MAP
SHOWS ALL THE BODIES OF WATER

20:56.777 --> 20:58.518
WITHIN A 50-MILE RADIUS
OF THE CRIME SCENE.

20:58.518 --> 21:01.129
RONALDO
PLANNED ON DIVING THEM ALL

21:01.129 --> 21:03.479
ONE BY ONE
IN THE HOPES OF FINDING IT.

21:03.479 --> 21:05.481
AND WHY WOULD HE THINK
THE GUN WAS THROWN
INTO A BODY OF WATER?

21:05.481 --> 21:07.831
I DON'T KNOW, BUT HE DID.

21:07.831 --> 21:10.965
AND THAT IS WHY THE KILLER
WANTED HIS BRIEFCASE --

21:10.965 --> 21:13.141
TO SEE HOW FAR RONALDO
HAD GOTTEN WITH HIS PLAN.

21:13.141 --> 21:15.143
THAT'S A PRETTY DESPERATE MOVE
ON RONALDO'S PART.

21:15.143 --> 21:17.972
I THINK "DESPERATE" MORE OR LESS
DESCRIBES THE WHOLE SITUATION.

21:17.972 --> 21:20.104
WELL, WE GOT 20 HOURS.
WHAT ARE WE SUPPOSED TO DO?

21:20.104 --> 21:21.845
WE'RE RIGHT WHERE
WE WANT TO BE.

21:21.845 --> 21:23.673
I'M GONNA NEED SOME HELP
FROM WYLIE,

21:23.673 --> 21:25.719
AND WE NEED TO SET UP
A SECURITY STATION

21:25.719 --> 21:27.373
DOWNSTAIRS IN THE LOBBY.WHY?

21:27.373 --> 21:29.375
WELL, WE ARE THE FBI.
SHOULDN'T WE BE SECURE?

21:29.375 --> 21:32.813
IF WE ARREST FEINBERG,
HE HAS TO STAY HERE, RIGHT?

21:32.813 --> 21:34.684
HE CAN'T JUST UP
AND LEAVE.

21:34.684 --> 21:36.469
JUST OVERNIGHT,
UNTIL HIS ARRAIGNMENT.

21:36.469 --> 21:38.297
OVERNIGHT IS PERFECT.

21:39.776 --> 21:40.864
WHAT ARE WE
ARRESTING HIM FOR?

21:50.918 --> 21:51.962
YES?

21:51.962 --> 21:53.442
EDWARD FEINBERG?
YES.

21:53.442 --> 21:57.185
SPECIAL AGENT CHO, FBI.
YOU'RE UNDER ARREST, SIR.

21:57.185 --> 21:59.013
FOR WHAT?PRESCRIPTION DRUG FRAUD.

21:59.013 --> 22:01.058
WE BELIEVE YOU'VE BEEN
SELLING PADS LIKE THIS
ONE TO DRUG USERS.

22:01.058 --> 22:02.538
WHERE DID YOU GET THAT?

22:02.538 --> 22:03.539
TURN AROUND, SIR.

22:03.539 --> 22:06.325
EDWARD?
WHAT'S GOING ON?

22:06.325 --> 22:07.891
I DON'T KNOW.

22:07.891 --> 22:10.241
CALL RICH SUMMERS.

22:10.241 --> 22:13.593
HAVE HIM MEET ME
AT THE FBI OFFICE.I'LL FOLLOW YOU.

22:22.079 --> 22:25.169
LET THE GAMES BEGIN.

22:31.872 --> 22:34.440
EMPTY YOUR POCKETS.
TAKE OFF YOUR WATCH, PLEASE.

22:34.440 --> 22:35.832
WHEN WILL I GET
THESE BACK?

22:35.832 --> 22:38.095
TOMORROW. WHEN YOU LEAVE
FOR YOUR ARRAIGNMENT.

22:38.095 --> 22:39.836
YOUR PURSE
AND CELLPHONE.

22:39.836 --> 22:41.795
I'M NOT UNDER ARREST.
WHY SHOULD I GIVE YOU MY PURSE?

22:41.795 --> 22:43.753
FBI POLICY.WELL, THAT'S CRAZY.

22:43.753 --> 22:45.581
YOU'RE FREE TO LEAVE
AT ANY TIME.

22:45.581 --> 22:47.322
BUT IF YOU WANT TO STAY, YOUR
PURSE AND CELLPHONE, PLEASE.

22:47.322 --> 22:49.759
YOU SHOULD GO.
THE ATTORNEY'S ON HIS WAY.

22:49.759 --> 22:51.979
NO. OF COURSE NOT.
I'M STAYING WITH YOU.

22:51.979 --> 22:55.069
STEP THROUGH, PLEASE.

23:04.121 --> 23:05.819
WAIT HERE, PLEASE.

23:17.744 --> 23:19.136
IT'S 5:00.

23:19.136 --> 23:20.964
EXCUSE ME?

23:20.964 --> 23:22.183
SORRY.
IT'S JUST...

23:22.183 --> 23:23.532
NEVER MIND.

23:23.532 --> 23:24.838
YOU MIGHT WANT TO COVER
YOUR EARS.

23:24.838 --> 23:26.013
WHY WOULD
I WANT TO DO THAT?

23:26.013 --> 23:27.275
[ FIRE ALARM BLARES ]

23:27.275 --> 23:29.451
THEY'RE TESTING
THE FIRE ALARM!

23:29.451 --> 23:31.845
IT GOES OFF TWICE A DAY,
AT 9:00 AND 5:00!

23:31.845 --> 23:33.194
[ BLARING STOPS ]

23:33.194 --> 23:35.022
IT'S GETTING PRETTY ANNOYING,
ACTUALLY.

23:35.022 --> 23:38.112
AGENT COLLINS, SHOW MR. FEINBERG
INTO INTERROGATION.

23:38.112 --> 23:39.548
SOMEONE
WILL BE IN SHORTLY.

23:41.637 --> 23:44.292
I --
CAN'T I GO WITH HIM?

23:44.292 --> 23:46.076
Fischer: NO, I'M SORRY.

23:46.076 --> 23:47.904
YOU'LL HAVE TO STAY IN
THE WAITING ROOM. COME WITH ME.

24:00.961 --> 24:03.398
YOU SHOULD BE COMFORTABLE ENOUGH
IN HERE.

24:03.398 --> 24:05.400
BATHROOMS
ARE AROUND THE CORNER.

24:05.400 --> 24:07.620
I HAVE TO STAY IN HERE?
FOR HOW LONG?

24:07.620 --> 24:11.188
I CAN SHOW YOU
TO YOUR OWN INTERROGATION ROOM

24:11.188 --> 24:13.277
IF YOU'D PREFER.

24:13.277 --> 24:15.584
NO. THAT'S FINE.

24:34.429 --> 24:36.649
HELLO.

24:36.649 --> 24:38.738
WHAT TIME IS IT?

24:38.738 --> 24:40.653
UM, 8:17.

24:40.653 --> 24:43.177
SORRY TO KEEP YOU WAITING
SO LONG.

24:43.177 --> 24:44.526
NONSENSE.

24:44.526 --> 24:46.223
YOU KEPT ME WAITING
ON PURPOSE,

24:46.223 --> 24:48.182
LIKE YOU TRUMPED UP
THIS DRUG CHARGE.

24:48.182 --> 24:51.141
LAST, DESPERATE ATTEMPT
TO PROVE YOUR PET THEORY.

24:52.447 --> 24:54.493
YOU KNOW, IT MUST BE VERY
DIFFICULT FOR PEOPLE AROUND YOU,

24:54.493 --> 24:56.233
THE FACT YOU CAN
NEVER ADMIT TO BEING WRONG.

24:56.233 --> 24:58.627
OKAY.

24:58.627 --> 25:00.847
WELL, LET'S CUT TO THE CHASE,
SHALL WE?

25:00.847 --> 25:03.371
IN 14 HOURS, LUIS CRUZ
IS GONNA BE EXECUTED

25:03.371 --> 25:05.112
FOR A CRIME
THAT YOU COMMITTED.

25:07.288 --> 25:09.899
I KNOW YOU THINK
YOU'RE DOING THE RIGHT THING.

25:09.899 --> 25:12.119
I MEAN,
IT'S ALWAYS THE HUSBAND, RIGHT?

25:12.119 --> 25:13.642
BUT IN THIS CASE,
IT'S NOT.

25:13.642 --> 25:14.730
SO YOU'VE SAID.

25:14.730 --> 25:16.340
FINE.
BELIEVE WHAT YOU WANT.

25:16.340 --> 25:18.952
I DIDN'T MURDER MY WIFE.YES, YOU DID.

25:18.952 --> 25:21.389
THEN YOU GOT IN YOUR CAR AND
YOU DROVE BACK TO YOUR OFFICE.

25:21.389 --> 25:23.609
YOU STOPPED ON THE WAY
AND YOU DUMPED THE GUN.

25:23.609 --> 25:25.524
NOW, YOU COULD HAVE
DUMPED IT ANYWHERE,

25:25.524 --> 25:27.613
BUT YOU CHOSE TO DUMP IT
IN A LAKE, WHICH IS A GOOD IDEA.

25:27.613 --> 25:29.092
GREAT HIDING SPOT.

25:29.092 --> 25:32.487
OF COURSE, UNTIL DAVID RONALDO
FIGURED IT OUT.

25:32.487 --> 25:34.054
RONALDO GOT YOUR GOAT,
DIDN'T HE?

25:34.054 --> 25:35.925
I DON'T EVEN KNOW
WHAT YOU MEAN.

25:35.925 --> 25:38.798
WELL, I MEAN THAT HE WASN'T
NEARLY AS CLEVER AS YOU,

25:38.798 --> 25:40.495
BUT HE WAS DETERMINED.

25:40.495 --> 25:44.455
HIS PERSISTENCE REALLY PAID OFF
FOR HIM, DIDN'T IT?

25:44.455 --> 25:45.935
WELL, YOU TELL ME.

25:45.935 --> 25:47.328
I WILL.

25:47.328 --> 25:49.286
THAT'S WHY YOU HIRED
THE PRIVATE DETECTIVE KOCH

25:49.286 --> 25:50.636
TO KEEP AN EYE ON HIM.

25:50.636 --> 25:51.941
AND YOU HAD HIM KILLED

25:51.941 --> 25:54.291
ONCE HE STARTED
TAKING DIVING LESSONS.

25:54.291 --> 25:56.598
THEN YOU HAD KOCH
GO THROUGH HIS BRIEFCASE

25:56.598 --> 25:58.295
TO SEE
WHAT EVIDENCE HE HAD,

25:58.295 --> 26:01.429
AND THEN YOU KILLED KOCH.

26:01.429 --> 26:03.562
THIS IS A VERY INTERESTING
THEORY.

26:03.562 --> 26:05.476
BUT EVEN
IF YOU FIND THE GUN,

26:05.476 --> 26:07.740
IT'S NOT GONNA PROVE
THAT I'M GUILTY.

26:07.740 --> 26:09.002
WELL, IT'S NOT GONNA HAVE

26:09.002 --> 26:10.873
ANY FINGERPRINTS ON IT,
OF COURSE,

26:10.873 --> 26:13.093
BUT IT MAY STILL HAVE
SERIAL NUMBERS ON IT,

26:13.093 --> 26:14.442
AND YOU
WOULD BE SURPRISED

26:14.442 --> 26:17.053
WHAT THE FBI CAN DO
WITH SERIAL NUMBERS.

26:17.053 --> 26:20.143
AND, OF COURSE, IT DOES PROVE
LUIS CRUZ'S INNOCENCE

26:20.143 --> 26:23.320
BECAUSE THE TIMELINE SUGGESTS
THAT THERE WAS NO WAY

26:23.320 --> 26:26.062
THAT HE COULD DUMP THE GUN
ANYWHERE

26:26.062 --> 26:29.109
BETWEEN YOUR HOUSE AND YOUR
OFFICE BEFORE HE WAS ARRESTED.

26:29.109 --> 26:30.589
WELL,
IT LOOKS LIKE YOU'VE GOT

26:30.589 --> 26:32.329
YOUR WORK CUT OUT FOR YOU NOW,
DOESN'T IT?

26:37.073 --> 26:40.555
MY NAME IS RICHARD SUMMERS.
I'M MR. FEINBERG'S ATTORNEY.

26:40.555 --> 26:43.210
I'LL BE SITTING IN FOR THE REST
OF THE INTERROGATION.

26:43.210 --> 26:44.733
WELL, I HOPE
FOR YOUR SAKE, RICHARD,

26:44.733 --> 26:46.213
THAT YOU'RE CHARGING HIM
BY THE HOUR

26:46.213 --> 26:47.693
'CAUSE IT'S GONNA BE
A LONG NIGHT.

26:47.693 --> 26:49.564
HERE'S HOW
THIS IS GONNA WORK.

26:49.564 --> 26:51.827
YOU CAN KEEP
MY CLIENT HERE OVERNIGHT,

26:51.827 --> 26:53.829
BUT HE'S NOT GONNA
SPEAK TO YOU.

26:53.829 --> 26:55.483
ABOUT ANYTHING.RICHARD --

26:55.483 --> 26:57.746
NOT ABOUT
THE PRESCRIPTION-DRUG MATTER,

26:57.746 --> 27:00.053
NOT ABOUT THE MURDER CASE.
NOTHING.

27:00.053 --> 27:01.532
ARE WE CLEAR?

27:01.532 --> 27:03.491
CRYSTAL.

27:03.491 --> 27:05.841
NOW I'D LIKE A MOMENT ALONE
WITH MY CLIENT.

27:18.854 --> 27:21.117
CHO, YOU'RE UP.

27:30.344 --> 27:32.825
I'M GONNA ASK YOU
SOME QUESTIONS.

27:32.825 --> 27:36.655
YOU CAN ASK ANYTHING YOU WANT.
HE'S NOT GONNA ANSWER YOU.

27:36.655 --> 27:38.308
I WANT TO HEAR IT
FROM HIM.

27:38.308 --> 27:41.094
WHERE WERE YOU ON THE NIGHT
OF FEBRUARY 11, 2000?

27:46.534 --> 27:48.797
I KNOW THIS IS HARD,
BUT I NEED TO TALK TO YOU

27:48.797 --> 27:50.451
ABOUT THE NIGHT
YOUR WIFE DIED.

27:50.451 --> 27:52.845
ANY LITTLE DETAIL
COULD HELP.

27:57.763 --> 27:59.373
Fischer:
LET'S JUST CHAT.

27:59.373 --> 28:01.331
HOW DO YOU LIKE
U.T. NEXT YEAR?

28:01.331 --> 28:05.161
I MEAN [SIGHS] I DON'T KNOW
ABOUT THEIR RUNNING GAME.

28:15.519 --> 28:17.783
[ SIGHS ]

28:17.783 --> 28:20.916
WELL, I HEAR
THE CAT'S GOT YOUR TONGUE.

28:20.916 --> 28:24.267
YOU THINK
YOU'LL LET SOMETHING SLIP?

28:24.267 --> 28:25.834
OKAY.

28:25.834 --> 28:28.663
I'M GONNA ASK YOU AGAIN.

28:28.663 --> 28:32.623
WHERE WERE YOU ON THE NIGHT
OF FEBRUARY 11, 2000,

28:32.623 --> 28:35.235
IN BETWEEN THE HOURS
OF 6:00 AND 9:00 P.M.?

28:35.235 --> 28:36.323
RICHARD?

28:36.323 --> 28:38.020
IS THIS NECESSARY?

28:38.020 --> 28:40.327
YOU KNOW
HE'S NOT GONNA DISCUSS IT.

28:40.327 --> 28:41.894
YES, IT'S NECESSARY,

28:41.894 --> 28:44.026
BECAUSE IN SEVEN HOURS,
A MAN IS GONNA DIE.

28:44.026 --> 28:46.725
YOU KNOW WHAT?
I RESENT --ED! DON'T.

28:49.902 --> 28:51.512
KIM,
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

28:51.512 --> 28:53.427
YOU'RE NOT GOING TO GET ANYTHING
OUT OF HIM TONIGHT.

28:53.427 --> 28:55.429
YOU MIGHT AS WELL
LET HIM REST.

28:55.429 --> 28:56.473
NO.

28:56.473 --> 28:58.084
DENNIS.

28:58.084 --> 28:59.259
YOU NEED TO REST.

28:59.259 --> 29:02.175
FINE.

29:02.175 --> 29:03.829
DON'T GET COMFORTABLE.

29:03.829 --> 29:05.221
I'LL BE BACK.

29:07.180 --> 29:09.312
I'LL BE TURNING OUT THE LIGHTS,
MR. SUMMERS,

29:09.312 --> 29:10.618
BUT YOU ARE WELCOME
TO STAY.

29:10.618 --> 29:13.360
ONLY ONE PILLOW, THOUGH.

29:13.360 --> 29:15.362
AND HOPEFULLY THE FLOOR
IS OKAY WITH YOU.

29:15.362 --> 29:18.104
I'M SURE IT'S BEEN CLEANED
SOMETIME IN THE PAST YEAR.

29:18.104 --> 29:19.148
LET'S HOPE.

29:19.148 --> 29:20.628
RICHARD,
YOU SHOULD GO.

29:20.628 --> 29:22.282
I WANT YOU RESTED
FOR MY ARRAIGNMENT.

29:22.282 --> 29:24.371
ARE YOU SURE?I WILL NOT SAY ANOTHER WORD

29:24.371 --> 29:25.851
UNTIL YOU GET BACK.
I PROMISE.

29:25.851 --> 29:27.200
GOOD.

29:27.200 --> 29:28.897
GET SOME REST.

29:41.736 --> 29:44.565
HI, THERE.
I BROUGHT YOU THIS.

29:44.565 --> 29:47.437
IS THIS FROM
THE FBI HANDBOOK?

29:47.437 --> 29:49.831
SOME GOOD COP/BAD COP
THING?

29:49.831 --> 29:51.180
[ CHUCKLES ]

29:51.180 --> 29:52.703
NO, IT'S JUST A PILLOW
AND A BLANKET.

29:52.703 --> 29:55.489
DO YOU HAVE ANY IDEA
WHAT YOU'RE DOING TO MY HUSBAND?

29:55.489 --> 29:56.969
YOU'RE ASKING HIM
TO RELIVE

29:56.969 --> 29:58.840
A VERY PAINFUL CHAPTER
IN HIS LIFE.

29:58.840 --> 30:01.669
I THINK IT WAS MORE PAINFUL
FOR SARAH.

30:01.669 --> 30:04.715
ANYWAY,
IT'LL ALL BE OVER SOON ENOUGH.

30:04.715 --> 30:06.369
6 1/2 HOURS, TO BE EXACT.

30:06.369 --> 30:08.937
YEAH, THEN WE'LL FINALLY HAVE
CLOSURE, NO THANKS TO YOU.

30:08.937 --> 30:12.767
NOW, IF YOU'LL EXCUSE ME,
I WOULD LIKE TO GET SOME REST.

30:14.856 --> 30:18.512
YOU NEEDN'T BE A MARTYR.
TAKE THE PILLOW.

30:43.929 --> 30:47.758
[ FIRE ALARM BLARES ]

30:47.758 --> 30:49.238
[ BLARING STOPS ]

30:54.635 --> 30:56.637
GOOD MORNING,
SLEEPYHEAD.

30:56.637 --> 30:58.639
[ SIGHS ]
WHAT TIME IS IT?

30:58.639 --> 31:01.642
IT'S A LITTLE AFTER 9:00.

31:01.642 --> 31:03.600
YOUR MURDEROUS ASS
GOT TO TAKE A NAP,

31:03.600 --> 31:05.994
WHILE ALL THE GOOD GUYS
HAD TO STAY UP ALL NIGHT.

31:05.994 --> 31:09.563
I TAKE IT
YOU DIDN'T FIND THE GUN.

31:09.563 --> 31:11.304
NO.

31:11.304 --> 31:14.655
SO THAT GIVES ME 40 MINUTES
TO GET YOU TO TALK.

31:14.655 --> 31:16.570
I WANT MY ATTORNEY.WE'LL CALL HIM.

31:16.570 --> 31:18.789
BUT FIRST, THE TRUTH.

31:18.789 --> 31:20.617
I HAVE NOTHING TO SAY.

31:24.404 --> 31:25.492
WE'LL SEE.

31:30.062 --> 31:31.759
IT'S 9:30.

31:31.759 --> 31:34.327
I'D LIKE TO KNOW HOW MUCH LONGER
YOU PLAN ON KEEPING US HERE.

31:34.327 --> 31:36.372
YOU'RE FREE TO GO
AT ANY TIME.

31:36.372 --> 31:38.853
BUT YOUR HUSBAND
WILL REMAIN IN CUSTODY

31:38.853 --> 31:40.333
UNTIL HIS ARRAIGNMENT.

31:40.333 --> 31:44.119
LOOK, I KNOW
THIS IS HARD ON YOU.

31:44.119 --> 31:45.599
YOU WANT A CUP OF COFFEE?

31:45.599 --> 31:48.036
YES, THANK YOU.

31:48.036 --> 31:50.734
I'M CHECKING IN
WITH THE DIVE UNIT.

31:50.734 --> 31:53.912
DAMN IT. TELL THEM
THEY'VE GOT 30 MINUTES.

31:53.912 --> 31:55.696
NOTHING YET.

31:55.696 --> 31:57.959
YOU'RE GONNA TALK TO ME!

31:57.959 --> 31:59.918
PLEASE.
I-I WANT MY ATTORNEY.

31:59.918 --> 32:01.441
IN THE NEXT FEW MINUTES,

32:01.441 --> 32:03.965
LUIS CRUZ IS GOING TO DIE
FOR YOUR CRIME.

32:03.965 --> 32:06.576
DOES THAT MEAN ANYTHING
TO YOU?

32:06.576 --> 32:08.230
A MAN'S DEATH?

32:08.230 --> 32:11.277
IS THAT ALL YOU'VE GOT?
APPEALS TO MY SYMPATHY?

32:11.277 --> 32:12.756
ANSWER THE QUESTION!

32:12.756 --> 32:15.020
IF HE WERE INNOCENT,
IT WOULD BE A TRAGEDY.

32:15.020 --> 32:16.543
BUT HE'S NOT.

32:16.543 --> 32:19.415
HE KILLED MY WIFE,
MY BEAUTIFUL, SWEET SARAH.

32:19.415 --> 32:22.853
HE DESERVES TO DIE.
I LOOK FORWARD IT.

32:22.853 --> 32:24.594
THERE YOU GO.

32:30.731 --> 32:32.167
FISCHER.

32:34.082 --> 32:35.692
[ SIGHS ]

32:35.692 --> 32:37.912
HE'S NOT TALKING.
IT'S ALL OVER.

32:37.912 --> 32:39.392
YOU CALLED
THE GOVERNOR'S OFFICE?

32:39.392 --> 32:40.959
I SPOKE TO AN AIDE.
NO GO.

32:40.959 --> 32:42.569
WITHOUT A WEAPON,
THEY'RE NOT GONNA POSTPONE.

32:42.569 --> 32:44.223
[ SIGHS ] CRAP.

32:44.223 --> 32:46.181
AND HE MADE IT
ABUNDANTLY CLEAR

32:46.181 --> 32:48.749
THAT ONCE CRUZ IS EXECUTED,
THE CASE IS DEAD.

32:48.749 --> 32:51.882
THEY'RE NOT GONNA WANT TO HEAR
ONE MORE WORD ABOUT IT.

32:51.882 --> 32:54.407
SO, WHAT NOW?

32:54.407 --> 32:56.887
COME ON.
EVERYONE'S WATCHING IT ON TV.

33:16.907 --> 33:18.387
I'M SORRY, PEOPLE.

33:18.387 --> 33:20.215
I WISH THIS HAPPENED
A DIFFERENT WAY.

33:21.608 --> 33:23.914
BOSS. LOOK.

33:28.180 --> 33:30.312
[ SIGHS ]

33:38.190 --> 33:40.540
WE DID WHAT WE COULD.

33:55.729 --> 33:57.774
CONGRATULATIONS.

33:57.774 --> 34:00.342
FOR WHAT?

34:00.342 --> 34:02.910
LUIS CRUZ IS DEAD.

34:11.701 --> 34:13.529
[ SIGHS ]

34:17.229 --> 34:19.361
WELL, THANK YOU
FOR TELLING ME.

34:19.361 --> 34:22.495
DOESN'T FEEL THE WAY
YOU THOUGHT IT WOULD, DOES IT?

34:22.495 --> 34:24.410
NO.

34:24.410 --> 34:28.805
NO, I THOUGHT I'D FEEL AVENGED,
OR AT LEAST RELIEVED.

34:28.805 --> 34:31.765
INSTEAD IT'S JUST SAD.

34:31.765 --> 34:35.029
AND IT DOESN'T BRING
MY WIFE BACK.

34:35.029 --> 34:38.728
NO. IT DOESN'T.

34:38.728 --> 34:41.862
I'M NOT SUPPOSED TO BE
TALKING TO YOU.

34:41.862 --> 34:44.125
AND I DON'T EVEN KNOW
WHY I SHOULD WANT TO.

34:44.125 --> 34:46.084
YOU THINK I'M A MURDERER.OH, I DON'T KNOW.

34:46.084 --> 34:47.433
I KNOW YOU DIDN'T KILL
YOUR WIFE.

34:47.433 --> 34:48.434
I KNEW ALL ALONG.

34:48.434 --> 34:49.783
WHAT?

34:49.783 --> 34:53.091
WELL, I STRONGLY SUSPECTED
YOU DIDN'T.

34:53.091 --> 34:55.876
AND YOUR REACTION
TO CRUZ'S DEATH PROVES IT.

34:55.876 --> 34:58.052
NOT THE REACTION
OF A GUILTY MAN.

34:59.749 --> 35:01.882
YOUR WIFE, MAE,
HOWEVER...

35:01.882 --> 35:03.449
WHAT ABOUT MAE?

35:03.449 --> 35:04.711
OH, COME ON.

35:04.711 --> 35:06.147
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

35:06.147 --> 35:08.280
I'LL LET YOU SEE
FOR YOURSELF.

35:15.156 --> 35:18.420
THIS IS HER
LEARNING OF THE EXECUTION.

35:29.562 --> 35:31.433
WELL,
THAT DOESN'T MEAN ANYTHING.

35:31.433 --> 35:33.740
COME ON, YOU CAN SEE IT.
IT'S OBVIOUS.NO, IT'S NOT OBVIOUS.

35:33.740 --> 35:35.959
WELL, IF YOU DIDN'T DO
IT AND LUIS CRUZ DIDN'T
DO IT, WHO DID IT?

35:35.959 --> 35:37.787
WHO WANTED
TO KILL YOUR WIFE?

35:37.787 --> 35:39.006
I-I DON'T --
I DON'T KNOW.

35:39.006 --> 35:40.790
MAE WORKED
AT THE CLINIC, RIGHT?

35:40.790 --> 35:43.141
VERY EASY FOR HER TO GET A PIECE
OF HIS CLOTHING.

35:43.141 --> 35:45.317
SHE DROVE TO YOUR HOUSE,
SHOT YOUR WIFE,

35:45.317 --> 35:47.536
AND LEFT HIS SWEATSHIRT
AT THE SCENE.

35:47.536 --> 35:50.104
THEN SHE DUMPED THE GUN
IN THE LAKE ON THE WAY HOME.

35:50.104 --> 35:51.671
NO, NO, NO, NO,
NO, NO, NO, NO.

35:51.671 --> 35:53.934
SHE KNEW YOU WERE NEVER GONNA
LEAVE YOUR WIFE,

35:53.934 --> 35:56.676
SO SHE TOOK CARE OF IT
FOR YOU.

35:57.416 --> 35:59.809
SHE WAS YOUR STUDENT,
YOUR LOVER.

35:59.809 --> 36:01.159
SHE IDOLIZED YOU.

36:01.159 --> 36:03.509
SHE WAS OBSESSED,
AND YOU KNEW THAT.

36:03.509 --> 36:05.511
BUT YOU ENJOYED
THE DEVOTION.

36:05.511 --> 36:07.208
IT FED YOUR EGO,

36:07.208 --> 36:10.342
SO YOU DIDN'T ALLOW YOURSELF
TO LOOK TOO CLOSELY.

36:10.342 --> 36:12.126
AND NOW AN INNOCENT MAN
IS DEAD.

36:12.126 --> 36:13.693
I DON'T BELIEVE
ANY OF THIS.

36:13.693 --> 36:15.347
AND SHE WAS THE ONE
WHO CONVINCED YOU

36:15.347 --> 36:17.610
TO KEEP THE AFFAIR A SECRET
AFTER YOUR WIFE DIED, RIGHT?

36:20.526 --> 36:22.223
YES.

36:22.223 --> 36:25.444
WHY DO YOU THINK SHE STAYED HERE
ALL NIGHT LAST NIGHT?

36:25.444 --> 36:27.620
TO SUPPORT YOU?
NO.

36:27.620 --> 36:30.188
BECAUSE SHE'S SCARED.

36:30.188 --> 36:32.364
SHE WANTS TO KNOW
WHAT WE HAVE.

36:32.364 --> 36:33.321
[ DOOR OPENS ]

36:33.321 --> 36:34.540
MR. FEINBERG,

36:34.540 --> 36:36.237
WE'RE DROPPING THE CHARGES
AGAINST YOU.

36:36.237 --> 36:37.673
YOU'RE FREE TO GO.

36:37.673 --> 36:40.198
THERE'S NO POINT NOW.
WE CAN'T MAKE A CASE.

36:40.198 --> 36:42.548
EDWARD,
THANK GOD.

36:49.555 --> 36:50.904
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

36:53.820 --> 36:55.909
EDWARD, WAIT!

36:55.909 --> 36:58.390
EDWARD, WHAT'S WRONG?
WHY ARE YOU IGNOR--

36:58.390 --> 37:00.261
LET ME HAVE THE KEYS.

37:00.261 --> 37:02.698
WELL,
WHAT DID THEY SAY?

37:02.698 --> 37:04.526
EDWARD, SPEAK TO ME.

37:04.526 --> 37:06.746
GIVE ME THE KEYS!

37:14.406 --> 37:16.059
MAE, I HAVE A QUESTION
FOR YOU,

37:16.059 --> 37:18.105
AND YOU NEED TO GIVE ME
AN HONEST ANSWER.

37:18.105 --> 37:20.063
YOU CAN ASK ME
ANYTHING.

37:20.063 --> 37:22.152
DID YOU KILL SARAH?

37:22.152 --> 37:25.417
WHAT?

37:25.417 --> 37:26.766
WHO TOLD YOU THAT?

37:26.766 --> 37:28.202
I NEED TO KNOW.
WAS IT YOU?

37:28.202 --> 37:29.943
OF COURSE NOT.

37:29.943 --> 37:32.032
I WOULD DIE
RATHER THAN HURT YOU.

37:34.034 --> 37:35.688
I DON'T BELIEVE YOU.

37:35.688 --> 37:37.429
DON'T SAY THAT.IT WAS YOU.

37:37.429 --> 37:39.300
EDWARD, STOP!
IT'S NOT TRUE!

37:39.300 --> 37:40.562
YOU KNEW
I'D NEVER LEAVE HER.

37:40.562 --> 37:42.129
W-- I LO-- I LOVE YOU.

37:42.129 --> 37:43.957
THAT DOESN'T MEAN
THAT I WOULD KILL THE WOMAN --

37:43.957 --> 37:46.089
DON'T LIE TO ME!PLEASE. YOU'RE SCARING ME.

37:46.089 --> 37:47.656
THIS IS INSANE.
YOU ARE INSANE.

37:47.656 --> 37:48.744
YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND!

37:48.744 --> 37:50.093
THEN EXPLAIN IT TO ME!

37:50.093 --> 37:53.575
I DID IT FOR US!

37:56.622 --> 37:58.319
SO WE COULD BE TOGETHER.

37:58.319 --> 37:59.799
OH, MY GOD.

37:59.799 --> 38:01.714
OH, MY GOD.
HOW COULD YOU HAVE DONE THIS?

38:01.714 --> 38:03.629
YOU HAVE TO BELIEVE ME.
IT WAS THE ONLY WAY.

38:03.629 --> 38:05.108
AND IT WORKED.
WE'RE TOGETHER.

38:05.108 --> 38:07.154
NOW THAT HE'S DEAD,
WE ARE SAFE.

38:07.154 --> 38:09.417
THERE IS NO ONE LOOKING
FOR THE KILLER.

38:09.417 --> 38:10.810
WE HAVE WEATHERED THE --

38:10.810 --> 38:12.594
DON'T TOUCH ME.

38:14.509 --> 38:16.424
WE HAVE WEATHERED
THE STORM.

38:16.424 --> 38:17.947
WE SHOULD BE CELEBRATING.

38:17.947 --> 38:21.255
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

38:26.782 --> 38:29.002
GET OUT OF THE CAR!
NOW!

38:32.875 --> 38:35.443
I DON'T UNDERSTAND.
WHAT'S GOING ON?

38:35.443 --> 38:36.923
Abbott:
YOU'RE UNDER ARREST

38:36.923 --> 38:39.012
FOR THE MURDER OF DAVID RONALDO,
SARAH FEINBERG,

38:39.012 --> 38:41.144
AND PETER KOCH.

38:41.144 --> 38:42.407
BUT LUIS CRUZ
KILLED SARAH.

38:42.407 --> 38:44.017
I MEAN,
HE WAS JUST EXECUTED FOR IT.

38:44.017 --> 38:45.584
WELL, ACTUALLY,
HE WASN'T.

38:45.584 --> 38:48.021
BUT THEY SAID ON THE NEWS --
IT HAPPENED AT 10:00.

38:49.327 --> 38:52.504
8:30.
I DON'T UNDERSTAND.

38:52.504 --> 38:55.245
YOU TRICKED ME?

38:55.245 --> 38:56.421
BINGO.

38:56.421 --> 38:58.684
YOU TOOK OUR PHONES,
HIS WATCH.

38:58.684 --> 39:00.338
Lisbon:
WE CHANGED ALL THE CLOCKS,

39:00.338 --> 39:01.774
INCLUDING YOUR CAR
AND CELLPHONE,

39:01.774 --> 39:02.905
WHILE YOU WERE SLEEPING.

39:02.905 --> 39:04.603
ACTUALLY,
YOU WOKE UP AT 7:00.

39:04.603 --> 39:07.170
THE TV --
THEY DID THAT, TOO?

39:07.170 --> 39:09.477
OH, NO. THAT WAS AGENT WYLIE.
I'M NOT MUCH WITH COMPUTERS.

39:09.477 --> 39:11.044
HE TOOK SOME FOOTAGE

39:11.044 --> 39:13.220
FROM EARLIER IN THE DAY
AND PUT A LITTLE BANNER ON IT.

39:13.220 --> 39:15.614
I DID, HOWEVER, PLANT THE BUG
IN YOUR HUSBAND'S POCKET

39:15.614 --> 39:18.747
THAT RECORDED EVERYTHING
THAT YOU SAID IN THE CAR.

39:20.183 --> 39:22.751
THIS IS FBI AGENT
DENNIS ABBOTT.

39:22.751 --> 39:25.363
I NEED TO SPEAK
TO THE GOVERNOR.

39:25.363 --> 39:27.843
FEELING A LITTLE SLEEPY?

39:29.584 --> 39:33.545
MAE FEINBERG GAVE UP
THE LOCATION OF THE GUN.

39:33.545 --> 39:36.852
IT WAS IN A POND
OFF OF I-35.

39:36.852 --> 39:40.290
SO THAT'S WHAT DAVID
WAS LOOKING FOR?

39:40.290 --> 39:42.075
YES.

39:42.075 --> 39:44.817
WE WOULDN'T HAVE BEEN ABLE
TO FIND IT WITHOUT HIM.

39:49.082 --> 39:51.693
HE DIED TRYING TO GET ME
OUT OF HERE.

39:51.693 --> 39:53.913
HE DID.

39:53.913 --> 39:56.089
LAWYERS ARE DOING
THEIR THING.

39:56.089 --> 39:58.439
IT'LL TAKE
A LITTLE WHILE.

39:58.439 --> 40:01.050
BUT THIS PROVES
YOU'RE INNOCENT, LUIS.

40:01.050 --> 40:03.401
YOU'LL BE WALKING
OUT OF HERE SOON.

40:21.288 --> 40:22.898
HOW'D IT GO?

40:22.898 --> 40:25.466
OH, WELL...

40:25.466 --> 40:27.990
IT'S NOT EVERY DAY
YOU GET TO TELL A MAN

40:27.990 --> 40:30.776
THAT HE'S GETTING OFF DEATH ROW
AND GOING HOME.

40:30.776 --> 40:32.778
IT WAS EMOTIONAL.

40:32.778 --> 40:34.693
I CAN IMAGINE.
MM-HMM.

40:34.693 --> 40:36.564
OH,
YOU'RE GONNA LIKE THIS.

40:36.564 --> 40:39.828
WE FOUND OUT HOW RONALDO KNEW
TO LOOK FOR THE GUN IN A POND.

40:39.828 --> 40:41.221
HE WENT TO A PSYCHIC.

40:41.221 --> 40:44.920
SHE SAID SHE SAW IT
NEAR A BODY OF WATER.

40:44.920 --> 40:46.139
PLEASE. COME ON.

40:46.139 --> 40:47.749
HOW MANY TIMES
DO I HAVE TO SAY IT?

40:47.749 --> 40:49.621
THERE'S NO SUCH THING
AS PSYCHICS.

40:49.621 --> 40:51.100
AND IT'S THE OLDEST ONE
IN THE BOOK.

40:51.100 --> 40:53.494
I MEAN,
IF YOU THINK ABOUT IT,

40:53.494 --> 40:56.497
MOST THINGS ARE CLOSE
TO A BODY OF WATER.

40:56.497 --> 40:57.977
YOU'RE JUST MAD
BECAUSE SHE WAS RIGHT.

40:57.977 --> 41:00.066
EVEN A BROKEN CLOCK

41:00.066 --> 41:04.374
GETS THE CHANCE TO BE RIGHT
TWICE A DAY.

41:04.374 --> 41:05.811
[ CHUCKLES ]

41:07.813 --> 41:10.206
OH, YEAH, THE WATER.

41:10.206 --> 41:12.948
[ WHISPERS INDISTINCTLY ]

41:18.432 --> 41:19.433
LOOK AT YOU.

41:19.433 --> 41:21.174
DON'T START.

41:21.174 --> 41:23.698
I'M NOT STARTING.
YOU LOOK BEAUTIFUL.

41:23.698 --> 41:26.179
I HOPE HE'S TAKING YOU
SOMEPLACE NICE.

41:26.179 --> 41:28.486
CLOTH NAPKINS
AND EVERYTHING.

41:28.486 --> 41:30.009
FANCY.
MM.

41:30.009 --> 41:31.880
WELL,
YOU HAVE A GREAT TIME.

41:33.969 --> 41:35.405
GOOD NIGHT, JANE.

41:41.107 --> 41:42.500
NIGHT, TERESA.

41:48.636 --> 41:49.637
[ SIGHS ]
